Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之菊…雪染同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜被擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是藍色的傢伙幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將他們全部幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還無法確認室長的安危嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 紅色的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被室長救了竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌亂保持秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種團體作戰下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人能勝過我們Scepter4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,室長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八咫烏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次來…做個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別給我東張西望的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想做個了斷…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是要先跟我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是應你的要求…才過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…那個的女人搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我閃邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對八田來說有點負擔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話倒是能和你玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 我現在沒這心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才就說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況我已經了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一旁閉嘴看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宗像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先躲在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人終於要交手了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩的必殺技對他們完全沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好他們打了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁這好機會 我們趕緊逃得遠遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理也救出來了 我們快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 沒辦法對你詳細說明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們會送你到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 不太疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但真沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來真的什麽都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠閒的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麽都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把所有責任都拋諸腦後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來你已經輸過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輸了 逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安穩的過日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實這才是你所期望的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在心底深處渴望過著這樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從以前…不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從更久以前就這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣默默的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃避嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 之後再來解決你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別動 馬上幫你處理傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡道別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃避嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宗像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標根本不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再打下去會讓我興奮起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色的…光？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又要發生什麽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是喜歡讓人大吃一驚的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 比起這個 你的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:56.48,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}別擔心 我…是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:03.31,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…果然是無色之王…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:15.18,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是阿道夫·K·威斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一王權者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白銀之王

